  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A gas tanker has arrived in the country - Litro Company",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro CEO has announced that a gas-carrying ship has arrived in the country.",
        "The Litro company has released a report on this and mentioned that 5 ships have arrived in the country so far in July alone.",
        "It is also noteworthy that Litro Company has also announced that 6 more ships will arrive in the country by the end of this month."
      ],
